# 
# aerc dracula styleset
# 
# This styleset uses the terminal defaults as its fallback.
# More information on how to configure the styleset can be found in
# the aerc-stylesets(7) manpage. Please read the manual before
# modifying or creating a styleset.
#
# Setting colors:
# default: The color is set as per the system or terminal default.
# <Color name>: Any w3c approved color name is used to set colors for the style.
# <Hex code>: Hexcode for a color can be used. The format must be #XXXXXX.
# <Dec number>: Color based on the terminal palette index. Valid numbers are between 0 and 255.

